      title="Software Engineer Intern"
      subtitle="From 2021 to 2022 at Tech Startup, City, Country"
    >
      Assisted in the development of a mobile application using React Native. Wrote unit and integration tests to ensure code quality. Participated in code reviews and agile ceremonies.
    </TimeLineElement>
  </div>

